---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Shout.com"
  description="Shout is a privacy-first platform for collecting feedback and improving experiences, where compliance is built into all features and tools."
>
  <div class="about-page">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Helping millions grow through feedback</h1>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">2001</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Launched</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">3,000,000+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Users</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Countries</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Shout Section -->
    <section class="what-is-shout-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What is Shout?</h2>
        <p class="section-description">
          At Shout, we help businesses connect with audiences. Whether you're capturing leads, collecting customer feedback, or measuring employee satisfaction, we provide the tools to track and improve experiences in one powerful app.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="mission-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="mission-content">
          <p>
            Having roots firmly placed in research and feedback, we know that listening to the people you matter most to your business is the only way to grow. But, with the growing number of data protection regulations around the world, collecting data isn't as simple as it once was.
          </p>
          <p>
            That's why we've re-built our software from the ground up, to make data collection as compliant as possible and remove some of that risk for businesses.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Core Platform Features -->
    <section class="platform-features-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>How Shout Works</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">üîó</div>
            <h3>Connect</h3>
            <p>Collect feedback and conduct research with surveys, generate leads and assess knowledge with quizzes, and capture new contacts with forms.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">üìä</div>
            <h3>Analyze</h3>
            <p>Use advanced filtering and crosstabulation tools to create unique views of your data and better understand your respondents.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Manage</h3>
            <p>Organize and segment your Shout CRM based on survey responses, email metrics, and contact data to personalize experiences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Integrated Tools Section -->
    <section class="tools-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Integrated tools to scale your business</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Shout's feedback platform makes it easy to collect data in a secure and compliant way. All tools are connected to your audience.
        </p>

        <div class="tools-grid">
          <div class="tool-card">
            <h4>Surveys</h4>
            <p>Our survey software allows you to collect omnidirectional feedback from respondents to help you make better business decisions.</p>
            <a href="/survey-maker/" class="tool-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-card">
            <h4>Quizzes</h4>
            <p>Our quiz builder has everything you need to engage audiences, generate leads, and assess staff and students.</p>
            <a href="/quiz-builder/" class="tool-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-card">
            <h4>Forms</h4>
            <p>Our form tools enable you to capture lead information, record consent, register guests, track incidents and much, much more.</p>
            <a href="/form-builder/" class="tool-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-card">
            <h4>CRM</h4>
            <p>Our integrated CRM lets you organize contacts in a way that works for your business, whilst ensuring you're compliant.</p>
            <a href="/crm/" class="tool-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-card">
            <h4>Reports</h4>
            <p>Our report dashboards give you a holistic view of all data associated with your campaigns, including responses and email metrics.</p>
            <a href="/reports/" class="tool-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy & Security Section -->
    <section class="privacy-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Privacy & Security</h2>
        <p class="privacy-intro">
          Shout is a privacy-first application, meaning data protection and security is engineered into all of our tools.
        </p>

        <div class="security-features">
          <div class="security-feature">
            <div class="security-icon">üîí</div>
            <h4>Zero-trust framework</h4>
            <p>We operate on a zero-trust security framework. This requires staff to be authenticated and validated to access applications and data.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="security-feature">
            <div class="security-icon">üè¢</div>
            <h4>UK based datacentres</h4>
            <p>Our main servers are located in the UK in a secure datacentre based on the ISO 27001:2013 security management standards.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="security-feature">
            <div class="security-icon">‚úÖ</div>
            <h4>Robust compliance standards</h4>
            <p>Our security policies are designed to meet or exceed the requirements of the GDPR, UK-GDPR, and CCPA.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Company Journey Section -->
    <section class="journey-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Journey</h2>
        <div class="journey-content">
          <div class="journey-item">
            <div class="journey-year">2001</div>
            <div class="journey-description">
              <h4>Foundation</h4>
              <p>Shout was founded with a focus on research and feedback collection, helping businesses understand their audiences.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="journey-item">
            <div class="journey-year">2020s</div>
            <div class="journey-description">
              <h4>Privacy-First Rebuild</h4>
              <p>Recognizing the changing landscape of data protection, we rebuilt our software from the ground up with compliance at its core.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="journey-item">
            <div class="journey-year">Today</div>
            <div class="journey-description">
              <h4>Global Impact</h4>
              <p>Now serving over 3 million users across 100+ countries, helping businesses grow through compliant feedback collection.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="values-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <h4>Privacy First</h4>
            <p>Every feature we build has privacy and compliance at its foundation, ensuring your data and your customers' data is protected.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h4>User-Centric Design</h4>
            <p>We believe great software should be intuitive and powerful, helping you achieve more without complexity.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h4>Continuous Innovation</h4>
            <p>We're constantly evolving our platform to meet the changing needs of businesses and regulatory requirements.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="value-card">
            <h4>Global Accessibility</h4>
            <p>Our tools are designed to work for businesses of all sizes, anywhere in the world, with localized compliance support.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to grow through feedback?</h2>
        <p>Join millions of users who trust Shout for their data collection and feedback needs.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/signup/" class="btn-primary">Start Your Free Trial</a>
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FBFBFB 0%, #F4F4F5 100%);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .stat {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Section Headings */
  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .section-description, .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    background: var(--background-light);
  }

  .mission-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mission-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Platform Features */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-pillar {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-pillar:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-pillar h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .feature-pillar p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Tools Section */
  .tools-section {
    background: var(--background-light);
  }

  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .tool-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .tool-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .tool-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .tool-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tool-link {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .tool-link:hover {
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  /* Privacy Section */
  .privacy-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .security-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .security-feature {
    background: white;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .security-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .security-feature h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .security-feature p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Journey Section */
  .journey-section {
    background: var(--background-light);
  }

  .journey-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .journey-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .journey-year {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    min-width: 100px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .journey-description h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .journey-description p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Values Section */
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .value-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid white;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .tools-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .security-features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .journey-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>